14 SECTION 1.9. Section 1.7 of this act applies to electronic wills executed on or after
15 January 1, 2026, and it further applies to attested written wills converted to electronic wills on or
16 after January 1, 2026, regardless of the date of execution of the attested written will. Section 1.7
17 of this act otherwise applies immediately to all wills deposited with the clerk at any time prior to
18 January 1, 2026. The remainder of this Part becomes effective January 1, 2026, and applies to
19 electronic wills executed on or after that date, and it further applies to attested written wills
20 converted to electronic wills on or after that date, regardless of the date of execution of the
21 attested written will.
